  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for all invoices matching and submissions</li><li>Perform data entry, coordination with various department</li><li>Manage daily workflow and ensuring that deadlines are met</li><li>Filling and update information in company systems and spreadsheets.</li><li>Record keeping</li><li>Ad-hoc duties assigned by superior</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma Qualification</li><li>Minimum 2-3 years of experiences in Finance or relevant experience</li><li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li><li>Able to converse in English and Chinese as needed to liaise with China associate.</li><li>Able to commence work with short notice</li><li>5.5 Working days per week*（Alternate Saturdays）</li></li></ul>",
